OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775235955
OL,3,CPolice helicopter joins search after
OL,4,Cprison van escape in Dorset
OL,6,FDorset Police are hunting for a man
OL,7,Fwho escaped from a prison van in Poole
OL,8,Fyesterday (Thursday 2nd April)
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,11,FJason Evans, 32, had appeared earlier
OL,12,Fin the day at Poole Magistrates' Court
OL,13,Fcharged with assault and was remanded
OL,14,Fin custody. He was being transported
OL,15,Fto another location by a privately-
OL,16,Foperated prison van when he made his
OL,17,Fescape on Poole Road at around 5:30pm.
OL,19,FOfficers started a ground and air
OL,20,Fsearch and brought in a police
OL,21,Fhelicopter to help scour the area.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
