FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775235955
OL,3,CPolice helicopter joins search after
OL,4,Cprison van escape in Dorset
OL,6,FEvans is described as white, five
OL,7,Ffight eight inches tall with ginger
OL,8,Fhair and was last spotted wearing grey
OL,9,Fclothing.
OL,11,FSuperintendent Joe Pardey from Dorset
OL,12,FPolice said, "I would like to reassure
OL,13,Fmembers of the public that we have
OL,14,Fofficers carrying out searches and
OL,15,Fother enquiries in a bid to locate
OL,16,FJason Evans as soon as possible and
OL,17,Freturn him to lawful custody.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
