OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775235955
OL,3,CPolice helicopter joins search after
OL,4,Cprison van escape in Dorset
OL,6,F"I would urge anyone who has seen a
OL,7,Fman in the area who matches the
OL,8,Fdescription given above and appears to
OL,9,Fbe avoiding detection to please come
OL,10,Fforward."
OL,12,FHe added: "We would ask the public not
OL,13,Fto approach him directly and to please
OL,14,Fdial 999 immediately.
OL,16,F"There will be an extensive police
OL,17,Fpresence in the area as we carry out
OL,18,Fthese enquiries and officers can be
OL,19,Fapproached by members of the community
OL,20,Fwith any concerns."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
